                    "text": "This matter comes before the Court on the Applicant's Motion (or Application) for Extension of Deadline for Submission of {{originalSubmissionName}}, filed by {{applicantName}}, Advocate for {{partyName}}, on {{applicationFiledDate}}.",
                    "style": "contentText"
                  },
                  {
                    "text": "WHEREAS, the Court, by Order {{orderId}} dated {{orderDate}}, set the deadline for submission of the {{originalSubmissionName}} as {{originalDeadlineDate}}; and",
