                    "text": "NOW, THEREFORE, IT IS HEREBY ORDERED that:",
                    "style": "contentText"
                  },
                  {
                    "ol": [
                      {
                        "text": "The Applicant's Motion (or Application) for Extension of Deadline for Submission of the {{originalSubmissionName}} is GRANTED.",
                        "style": "contentText"
                      },
                      {
                        "text": "The deadline for submission of the {{originalSubmissionName}} is EXTENDED from {{originalDeadlineDate}} to {{newDeadlineDate}}.",
